latestIgtvVideos.caption:
My FIRST and probably last “makeup tutorial” for @brownsfashion thanks for inviting me to be apart of your family @ibkamara 🖤
I created a sexy 70s makeup look to go with this @bottegaveneta dress.
Thank you my beautiful friends for doing this with me I feel truly blessed to have such talented creative visionary people in my life💓💓💓

Shot and edited by @deadhungry
Music @lafawndah_
Hair @alipirzadeh using @apwigs
Nails @sylviemacmillan.nails using @cndworld 
🖤 #afamilyaffair #family4life 🖤
